26
00:01:18,879 --> 00:01:19,920
Promise me.

27
00:01:21,239 --> 00:01:23,000
Keep this child.

28
00:01:25,000 --> 00:01:26,840
If anything happens to you,

29
00:01:26,840 --> 00:01:29,560
