34
00:02:00,868 --> 00:02:05,396
=Episode 2=

35
00:02:34,039 --> 00:02:35,919
Is it you?

36
00:02:44,159 --> 00:02:46,319
I knew you'd come back.

37
00:02:48,039 --> 00:02:50,479
I knew you'd definitely come back.

38
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,840
They said the army you joined

39
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:57,800
was wiped out in the first battle.

40
00:02:58,919 --> 00:03:00,360
But I don't believe it.

41
00:03:01,439 --> 00:03:03,199
I don't believe it at all.

42
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,199
Wake up.

43
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,960
Don't faint. Wake up.

44
00:03:29,319 --> 00:03:31,240
Push harder.

45
00:03:31,439 --> 00:03:34,080
Very good. Come on.

46
00:03:34,080 --> 00:03:35,120
Hot water.

47
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,639
Get a new tub of water.

48
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:38,879
Hurry. Take a deep breath.

49
00:03:38,879 --> 00:03:40,879
Good. It's almost out.

50
00:03:40,879 --> 00:03:42,280
Push harder.

51
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,039
Put the medicine here.

52
00:03:44,039 --> 00:03:45,599
Give me a clean cloth.

53
00:03:45,599 --> 00:03:46,879
Change the water.

54
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:48,439
I can see the head.

55
00:03:48,439 --> 00:03:49,719
It's out.

56
00:03:50,599 --> 00:03:53,199
Get more haemostatic cloths.

57
00:03:53,199 --> 00:03:54,000
Hurry up.

58
00:04:04,280 --> 00:04:05,879
It's out.

59
00:04:05,879 --> 00:04:08,080
It's a boy.

60
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,000
