61
00:04:17,399 --> 00:04:18,120
Look at him.

62
00:04:18,120 --> 00:04:20,720
Doesn't the child look exactly
like the young master?

63
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:22,000
Look at his face.

64
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:23,839
His eyebrows are exactly alike.

65
00:04:46,519 --> 00:04:48,720
