68
00:04:56,040 --> 00:04:57,279
Thank you, Matriarch.

69
00:04:57,480 --> 00:04:59,439
It's a real blessing for our family.

70
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,040
(Mrs. Wu)
Shameless.

71
00:05:02,279 --> 00:05:03,560
