a substitute for her man!

73
00:05:07,439 --> 00:05:08,920
(Mrs. Rong of the Third Branch)
Great.

74
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,240
She has a son.

75
00:05:11,839 --> 00:05:14,040
Now Matriarch can't kick
her out of the house.

76
00:05:14,319 --> 00:05:15,560
And to make matters worse,

77
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:17,319
not only will she not get divorced,

78
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:20,639
but she will also be
in charge of the Rong Family.

79
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:31,839
Matriarch,

80
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:34,519
