81
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:36,240
He can't be the heir.

82
00:05:36,439 --> 00:05:37,680
The heir to their family property

83
00:05:37,680 --> 00:05:40,199
must be her own son.

84
00:05:40,941 --> 00:05:43,718
(Matriarch Rong)

85
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:49,959
I have promised Lingyi

86
00:05:49,959 --> 00:05:52,759
to register the child under her name

87
00:05:53,319 --> 00:05:56,040
as their legitimate son.

88
00:06:00,759 --> 00:06:02,120
Thank you, Matriarch.

89
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:06,319
I have already sent a letter
to our family head.

90
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:10,040
Once they arrive tomorrow,
bring the child over.

91
00:06:10,040 --> 00:06:12,120
A ceremony will be held
at the ancestral temple.

92
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:28,480
Lady, don't sit there.

93
00:06:28,480 --> 00:06:30,199
The stone is cold. Please rise.

94
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:32,399
You just gave birth.

95
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:34,120
A woman has to take good care of herself

96
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:35,920
after childbirth.

97
00:06:37,519 --> 00:06:38,319
Lady,

98
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:40,120
you came here for prenatal care.

99
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:43,879
We were specifically warned not
to ask too much about your affairs.

100
00:06:43,879 --> 00:06:46,040
But please allow me to ask.

101
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,319
Why hasn't the father of the child

102
00:06:47,319 --> 00:06:49,000
ever come to see you?

103
00:06:50,160 --> 00:06:52,000
I didn't come here for prenatal care.

104
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:54,120
I got pregnant

105
00:06:55,519 --> 00:06:57,279
after I came here.

106
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,639
It's weird.

107
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:00,920
We were told to prepare
nourishment for gestation

108
00:07:00,920 --> 00:07:03,439
before you'd been here for a month.

109
00:07:03,439 --> 00:07:06,560
But it would take at least a month

110
00:07:06,560 --> 00:07:08,399
to know of a pregnancy.

111
00:07:09,439 --> 00:07:10,519
What does it mean?

112
00:07:11,319 --> 00:07:12,439
Are you saying

113
00:07:12,879 --> 00:07:14,199
if the pregnancy is confirmed,

114
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:18,639
the woman must have been pregnant
for over a month?

115
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,319
Yeah.

116
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:22,639
I've had several children.

117
00:07:22,639 --> 00:07:23,879
That's what many doctors

118
00:07:23,879 --> 00:07:25,199
I've seen told me.

119
00:07:25,399 --> 00:07:26,199
My lady,

120
00:07:26,199 --> 00:07:28,360
do you remember when you had

121
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,360
