122
00:07:38,519 --> 00:07:39,480
Are you okay?

123
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,480
They tricked me!

124
00:07:45,639 --> 00:07:46,480
The baby...

125
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:49,480
The baby is my husband's.

126
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,279
My beloved,

127
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:58,319
