132
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,800
Something's wrong.

133
00:08:14,839 --> 00:08:15,399
Just now...

134
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:19,399
Just now, someone saw
Xue Wan'er taking the baby away.

135
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,319
